<span class="p_del">-	/*</span>
<span class="p_del">-	 * Stack looks like this:</span>
<span class="p_del">-	 * Address	Contents</span>
<span class="p_del">-	 * esp		EIP</span>
<span class="p_del">-	 * esp + 4	CS</span>
