<span class="p_del">-	 */</span>
<span class="p_del">-	release_pte(*spte);</span>
<span class="p_del">-</span>
<span class="p_del">-	/*</span>
<span class="p_del">-	 * If this is a write, we insist that the Guest page is writable (the</span>
